{"title":"Cane Creek Galaxy Helm Sparkles Bright for a Fortnight","link":"https://bikerumor.com/cane-creek-galaxy-helm-sparkles-bright-for-a-fortnight/","date":1689685200000,"content":"<p>OK, so it might be around for more than a couple weeks, but the latest limited edition Cane Creek Helm fork is available while supplies last, then it’s only going to shine on those riders’ bikes who grabbed one early.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Built off the same chassis as their current Helm MKII, the Galaxy edition gets a holographic ultraviolet glitter that gives it a color-changing effect as it goes by.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3.jpg\" alt=\"cane creek galaxy helm fork with sparkle paint shown on a mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-3-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It comes in 29er only with air (2,080g) or coil (2,340g) springs and Boost spacing. Travel is preset at 160mm but can be easily adjusted in 10mm increments all the way down to 100mm for air springs, and 130mm with coil springs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It comes with 35mm stanchions, 44mm offset, and their excellent damping system and SKF seals for plush, well-controlled performance that’s made it one of our favorites around the Bikerumor offices.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1286\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-1.jpg\" alt=\"cane creek galaxy helm fork with sparkle paint\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-1.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-1-297x191.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-1-800x514.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-1-120x77.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-1-768x494.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/canecreek-helm-galaxy-sparkle-paint-limited-edition-1-1536x988.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Air volume is also adjustable, and it’s unique system for setting negative spring pressure (on the air forks) allows for a bit of fine tuning between the chambers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>MSRP is $1,099 and includes the Helm fender. Check our <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-cane-creek-helm-mkii-suspension-fork-is-lookin-smooth-in-all-black-limited-edition-pink/\" target=\"_blank\">launch coverage</a> for more tech details on the internals, and past special edition colors <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/limited-edition-cane-creek-helm-mkii-sunburst-29er-fork-lights-things-up/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/limited-edition-cane-creek-helm-chameleon-shines-good-trail-karma-likely/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://canecreek.com\" target=\"_blank\">CaneCreek.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/cane-creek-galaxy-helm-sparkles-bright-for-a-fortnight/\">Cane Creek Galaxy Helm Sparkles Bright for a Fortnight</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"a9170d686831b2e3db051a2ca776cadc289fcdbc9563b7ad1deb73783bc1becd","category":"Cycling"}